678
00:30:52.270 --> 00:30:54.312 line:80%
Brother, why don't you make a pledge, huh?

679
00:30:54.604 --> 00:30:55.979 line:80%
Who knows, it might work for you too.

680
00:30:56.520 --> 00:30:57.770 line:80%
- What do you say, Uncle?
- Yeah, why not?

681
00:30:59.020 --> 00:31:00.812 line:80%
I've tried trusting one Bhagwan before.

682
00:31:01.145 --> 00:31:02.312 line:80%
I can't do it again.

683
00:31:02.687 --> 00:31:06.020 line:80%
What's the point of sitting like this
and giving up, Nephew?

684
00:31:06.270 --> 00:31:07.604 line:80%
Give it a try.

685
00:31:08.520 --> 00:31:09.854 line:80%
Uncle, I don't want to try.

686
00:31:10.062 --> 00:31:11.104 line:80%
You try it.

687
00:31:11.520 --> 00:31:13.687 line:80%
What's the harm in trying once, huh?

688
00:31:13.770 --> 00:31:14.937 line:80%
Try it.

689
00:31:15.854 --> 00:31:17.687 line:80%
Do you have money to pay the bill?
He's gone.

690
00:31:17.979 --> 00:31:19.270 line:80%
You don't have any?

691
00:31:22.812 --> 00:31:23.979 line:80%
Glory to Lord Shiva!

692
00:31:24.187 --> 00:31:26.979 line:80%
Praise be to the consort
of Goddess Parvati!

693
00:31:27.062 --> 00:31:31.020 line:80%
Har Har Mahadev!

694
00:31:32.562 --> 00:31:33.770 line:80%
Dear Mahadev,

695
00:31:33.854 --> 00:31:35.645 line:80%
please grant me a government job quickly.

696
00:31:35.729 --> 00:31:37.937 line:80%
I pledge I'll shave my head...

697
00:31:38.604 --> 00:31:40.895 line:80%
No, if I shave my head,
everyone will think my dad's dead.

698
00:31:41.145 --> 00:31:42.645 line:80%
No, I can't shave my head.

699
00:31:43.145 --> 00:31:45.604 line:80%
Dear Mahadev,
please give me a government job quickly.

700
00:31:45.687 --> 00:31:48.270 line:80%
I pledge I'll fast for 16 Mondays...

701
00:31:48.895 --> 00:31:50.812 line:80%
Girls do that to find a good husband.

702
00:31:51.020 --> 00:31:53.104 line:80%
And I'm going to be a good husband,
Mahadev.

703
00:31:53.354 --> 00:31:55.562 line:80%
What should I say?
Mahadev, Mahadev...

704
00:31:55.854 --> 00:31:57.729 line:80%
Dear Mahadev,
please give me a government job quickly.

705
00:31:57.812 --> 00:32:01.145 line:80%
I pledge to remain celibate for life.

706
00:32:01.895 --> 00:32:02.854 line:80%
Celibate?

707
00:32:03.062 --> 00:32:04.979 line:80%
I want the job so I can get married!

708
00:32:05.229 --> 00:32:07.270 line:80%
Are you making a vow
or playing KBC with God?

709
00:32:07.354 --> 00:32:08.979 line:80%
Can't you see there's
a long line behind you?

710
00:32:09.062 --> 00:32:10.854 line:80%
Give me just two minutes, Brother.

711
00:32:11.187 --> 00:32:12.562 line:80%
He wants two minutes!

712
00:32:12.937 --> 00:32:14.854 line:80%
Mahadev, I'll be right back, okay?

713
00:32:15.645 --> 00:32:17.687 line:80%
- Go, take His blessings.
- Get out of my way.

714
00:32:21.520 --> 00:32:23.520 line:80%
Pundit-ji, I seek your blessings.

715
00:32:23.645 --> 00:32:24.645 line:80%
Mahadev!

716
00:32:25.854 --> 00:32:28.020 line:80%
Pundit-ji, I wanted to ask you something.

717
00:32:29.229 --> 00:32:32.604 line:80%
What pledge should I make
to ensure God answers my wish?

718
00:32:34.812 --> 00:32:36.062 line:80%
Why are you laughing?

719
00:32:37.020 --> 00:32:38.312 line:80%
My life's a mess.

720
00:32:38.979 --> 00:32:42.187 line:80%
What can you give God
when you're here asking for help?

721
00:32:44.479 --> 00:32:47.854 line:80%
But I've heard that God doesn't
listen unless you offer something.

722
00:32:47.979 --> 00:32:49.145 line:80%
Do you think

723
00:32:49.979 --> 00:32:54.187 line:80%
God will listen faster
if you offer something?

724
00:32:54.937 --> 00:32:57.562 line:80%
So, what should I do to make
God answer my prayers, Pundit-ji?

725
00:32:58.770 --> 00:32:59.979 line:80%
Give Rs. 101.

726
00:33:00.437 --> 00:33:01.937 line:80%
He'll fulfill it for just Rs. 101?

727
00:33:01.979 --> 00:33:02.895 line:80%
Mahadev!

728
00:33:02.979 --> 00:33:05.062 line:80%
That's my fee, son.

729
00:33:06.354 --> 00:33:07.562 line:80%
Oh, for you.

730
00:33:10.229 --> 00:33:11.104 line:80%
Keep it here.

731
00:33:14.145 --> 00:33:15.937 line:80%
I'll pay you Re. 1 through UPI.

732
00:33:16.479 --> 00:33:17.604 line:80%
Please, tell me.

733
00:33:18.395 --> 00:33:20.937 line:80%
Son, go outside, get some milk,

734
00:33:21.937 --> 00:33:25.604 line:80%
offer it to Mahadev with a clean heart

735
00:33:26.062 --> 00:33:29.979 line:80%
and pledge that if He fulfills your wish,

736
00:33:30.062 --> 00:33:31.979 line:80%
you'll do a good deed.

737
00:33:32.812 --> 00:33:33.895 line:80%
- That's it?
- Yes.

738
00:33:33.979 --> 00:33:35.104 line:80%
- Just offer Him milk?
- Yes.

739
00:33:36.354 --> 00:33:37.770 line:80%
- Goodbye, Pundit-ji.
- Stay happy.

740
00:33:37.895 --> 00:33:41.270 line:80%
Pundit-ji, whose milk should
I offer-cow, buffalo, or goat?

741
00:33:41.770 --> 00:33:42.729 line:80%
Cow.

742
00:33:42.812 --> 00:33:43.812 line:80%
Cow's milk.

743
00:33:43.895 --> 00:33:44.979 line:80%
Goodbye, Pundit-ji.

744
00:33:49.812 --> 00:33:50.979 line:80%
Work faster.

745
00:33:51.020 --> 00:33:52.270 line:80%
We've got a huge order.

746
00:33:53.520 --> 00:33:56.520 line:80%
Oh no, Shahida,

747
00:33:56.604 --> 00:33:59.520 line:80%
you're cutting them
too big-make them smaller.

748
00:33:59.604 --> 00:34:00.645 line:80%
Will this size work?

749
00:34:00.729 --> 00:34:03.854 line:80%
No, smaller than that.
You're not understanding.

750
00:34:03.979 --> 00:34:04.687 line:80%
Cut them smaller.

751
00:34:04.770 --> 00:34:05.854 line:80%
She wants us to smash them?

752
00:34:05.937 --> 00:34:08.604 line:80%
They just don't get it.
Should I crush them?

753
00:34:09.479 --> 00:34:10.937 line:80%
Come on, son,

754
00:34:10.979 --> 00:34:13.187 line:80%
- why the long face?
- Take it off.

755
00:34:13.270 --> 00:34:15.187 line:80%
You'll find another job.

756
00:34:16.520 --> 00:34:17.770 line:80%
And another girl too.

757
00:34:18.604 --> 00:34:19.520 line:80%
Yes.

758
00:34:19.604 --> 00:34:20.687 line:80%
Come on.

759
00:34:35.979 --> 00:34:37.937 line:80%
Look at this pickle, for example.

760
00:34:38.354 --> 00:34:40.062 line:80%
It takes a lot of effort.

761
00:34:40.520 --> 00:34:41.979 line:80%
We cut them, dry them,

762
00:34:42.020 --> 00:34:45.187 line:80%
oil them, rub spices on them,
pack them in a jar.

763
00:34:45.979 --> 00:34:48.020 line:80%
But one drop of water,

764
00:34:49.270 --> 00:34:50.645 line:80%
and it's ruined.

765
00:34:51.437 --> 00:34:54.020 line:80%
But that doesn't mean
we stop making pickles.

766
00:34:54.687 --> 00:34:56.562 line:80%
I've built a huge business out of this.

767
00:34:58.937 --> 00:35:00.937 line:80%
Life's the same.

768
00:35:02.562 --> 00:35:04.562 line:80%
Some things work out, others don't.

769
00:35:04.729 --> 00:35:05.604 line:80%
Got it?

770
00:35:05.812 --> 00:35:08.604 line:80%
But that doesn't mean you stop living.

771
00:35:10.770 --> 00:35:13.145 line:80%
Just stay away from water drops, like him.

772
00:35:13.812 --> 00:35:16.104 line:80%
Always doing these breathing exercises.

773
00:35:16.729 --> 00:35:17.562 line:80%
Answer it.

774
00:35:17.645 --> 00:35:19.645 line:80%
Your pain in the neck
phone's ringing, answer it.

775
00:35:20.895 --> 00:35:21.770 line:80%
Let it ring.

776
00:35:21.854 --> 00:35:24.520 line:80%
If you don't want to answer,
just disconnect it.

777
00:35:25.604 --> 00:35:26.770 line:80%
What are you staring at?

778
00:35:26.937 --> 00:35:28.604 line:80%
What did I tell you?

779
00:35:29.312 --> 00:35:31.187 line:80%
What did I tell you?
Look, you need to do it like this.

780
00:35:31.854 --> 00:35:33.270 line:80%
Breathe in from the right.

781
00:35:33.354 --> 00:35:34.145 line:80%
Hello?

782
00:35:34.854 --> 00:35:35.854 line:80%
Where are you?

783
00:35:36.104 --> 00:35:37.729 line:80%
I've been trying to reach you.

784
00:35:37.895 --> 00:35:39.062 line:80%
Life's been trying me too.

785
00:35:39.354 --> 00:35:40.187 line:80%
Who is this?

786
00:35:40.270 --> 00:35:42.104 line:80%
It's me, Bhagwan.
Have you forgotten me already?

787
00:35:43.062 --> 00:35:44.312 line:80%
You...

788
00:35:44.604 --> 00:35:45.937 line:80%
You're a demon!

789
00:35:46.312 --> 00:35:47.979 line:80%
I'm going to kill you!
Where the hell are you?

790
00:35:48.020 --> 00:35:49.937 line:80%
This is great, son.
You want to kill me after

791
00:35:49.979 --> 00:35:51.770 line:80%
I went all the way to Lucknow for you?

792
00:35:52.229 --> 00:35:54.020 line:80%
It was tough, but I handled it.

793
00:35:55.645 --> 00:35:56.479 line:80%
Handled it?

794
00:35:56.687 --> 00:35:59.854 line:80%
I mean, your government job's confirmed.

795
00:35:59.937 --> 00:36:01.354 line:80%
Do you even check your emails?

796
00:36:01.854 --> 00:36:02.729 line:80%
Huh?

797
00:36:02.812 --> 00:36:05.312 line:80%
Stop all this and arrange
Rs. 600,000, understood?

798
00:36:05.604 --> 00:36:06.687 line:80%
Hang up now.

799
00:36:06.979 --> 00:36:07.937 line:80%
Hello?

800
00:36:09.979 --> 00:36:10.979 line:80%
What happened?

801
00:36:12.979 --> 00:36:14.729 line:80%
Well, I...

802
00:36:16.229 --> 00:36:17.687 line:80%
I got a government job.

803
00:36:17.770 --> 00:36:18.729 line:80%
Huh?

804
00:36:18.937 --> 00:36:19.937 line:80%
Nonsense!

805
00:36:21.145 --> 00:36:23.354 line:80%
- I got a job, Dad!
- Get off me.

806
00:36:23.437 --> 00:36:25.937 line:80%
Mom, I got a government job!

807
00:36:28.812 --> 00:36:30.854 line:80%
- Sister-in-law, you're not eating.
- Try these.

808
00:36:30.937 --> 00:36:32.229 line:80%
Have some
Ladoos
.

809
00:36:32.895 --> 00:36:33.979 line:80%
Have it.

810
00:36:36.812 --> 00:36:41.937 line:80%
Brother, why don't my son
and your daughter talk privately?

811
00:36:42.520 --> 00:36:46.020 line:80%
- Sure, why not?
- Go, Titli, show Chunne your room.

812
00:36:47.520 --> 00:36:50.229 line:80%
I'm not showing
that buffoon my room, okay?

813
00:36:50.312 --> 00:36:51.854 line:80%
He's a good guy.

814
00:36:51.937 --> 00:36:53.187 line:80%
She's just a little shy.

815
00:36:53.895 --> 00:36:54.895 line:80%
Her nature shows it -

816
00:36:54.979 --> 00:36:56.770 line:80%
- she's quiet and calm.
- Yes, she is.

817
00:36:56.854 --> 00:36:58.979 line:80%
It's a blessing from God,
we feel really blessed.

818
00:36:59.062 --> 00:37:00.020 line:80%
Move!

819
00:37:00.354 --> 00:37:04.437 line:80%
I was wondering
what's been vibrating under me.

820
00:37:05.145 --> 00:37:07.020 line:80%
- That's Titli's phone.
- Go get it.

821
00:37:07.104 --> 00:37:10.104 line:80%
Okay.
Someone named Babu is calling.

822
00:37:10.187 --> 00:37:13.812 line:80%
She's Titli's childhood friend.

823
00:37:13.895 --> 00:37:14.854 line:80%
Babli.

824
00:37:14.937 --> 00:37:15.937 line:80%
I see.

825
00:37:16.145 --> 00:37:17.854 line:80%
- Yes.
- I thought...

826
00:37:18.229 --> 00:37:21.520 line:80%
- No, it's not like that.
- Pundit-ji, set the wedding date.

827
00:37:21.854 --> 00:37:22.937 line:80%
Why are you calling?

828
00:37:22.979 --> 00:37:23.937 line:80%
A prospective groom's family
is here to meet her.

829
00:37:23.979 --> 00:37:24.687 line:80%
Hang up the phone.

830
00:37:24.770 --> 00:37:26.604 line:80%
Sister, start the wedding preparations.

831
00:37:27.270 --> 00:37:30.270 line:80%
Tell Titli and her dad
I got a government job.

832
00:37:30.687 --> 00:37:31.562 line:80%
- What are you saying?
- Yes.

833
00:37:31.645 --> 00:37:32.979 line:80%
Give me a moment, I'll tell her.

834
00:37:33.020 --> 00:37:35.020 line:80%
- I'll give you the opportunity to...
- Titli!

835
00:37:36.520 --> 00:37:37.854 line:80%
Ranjan got the job.

836
00:37:37.937 --> 00:37:38.645 line:80%
What?!

837
00:37:39.187 --> 00:37:40.604 line:80%
Let me talk to him.

838
00:37:41.020 --> 00:37:42.020 line:80%
- What happened?
- Yes, Babu...

839
00:37:42.104 --> 00:37:43.229 line:80%
- Nothing.
- What's going on?

840
00:37:43.312 --> 00:37:44.770 line:80%
- I'll tell him...
- Brother, hurry up.

841
00:37:44.854 --> 00:37:45.979 line:80%
Why don't you just start dwelling
in my ears, huh!

842
00:37:46.062 --> 00:37:47.229 line:80%
I'm working on it.

843
00:37:47.729 --> 00:37:49.104 line:80%
- Dad!
- What?

844
00:37:49.437 --> 00:37:52.020 line:80%
Ranjan got a government job!

845
00:37:53.604 --> 00:37:54.937 line:80%
Who's Ranjan?

846
00:37:55.937 --> 00:37:56.937 line:80%
No.

847
00:37:57.604 --> 00:37:59.020 line:80%
We can't do anything now.

848
00:37:59.645 --> 00:38:00.895 line:80%
His time is up.

849
00:38:01.104 --> 00:38:03.187 line:80%
You'll marry Chunne.

850
00:38:03.479 --> 00:38:05.562 line:80%
My name is Anoop.

851
00:38:05.645 --> 00:38:07.020 line:80%
Yes, Anoop Chunne.

852
00:38:09.187 --> 00:38:12.937 line:80%
So things got delayed by a few days.
What's the big deal, Dad?

853
00:38:13.062 --> 00:38:14.104 line:80%
What, Dad, huh?

854
00:38:14.437 --> 00:38:16.604 line:80%
I'm not going to marry
this laughing stock!

855
00:38:17.270 --> 00:38:21.145 line:80%
Mr. Mishra, your daughter
is calling my son a laughing stock!

856
00:38:21.562 --> 00:38:22.895 line:80%
- This isn't right.
- No, I...

857
00:38:22.979 --> 00:38:23.979 line:80%
Listen to me...

858
00:38:25.062 --> 00:38:26.937 line:80%
What's not right, Uncle?

859
00:38:27.895 --> 00:38:30.687 line:80%
Be thankful we didn't get married.

860
00:38:30.979 --> 00:38:35.937 line:80%
Otherwise, I'd make your life
and your son's life a living hell!

861
00:38:36.145 --> 00:38:37.562 line:80%
Got it?

862
00:38:37.895 --> 00:38:38.729 line:80%
And yours too.

863
00:38:38.812 --> 00:38:39.770 line:80%
Mr. Mishra...

864
00:38:40.354 --> 00:38:41.645 line:80%
Why are you misbehaving?

865
00:38:42.937 --> 00:38:44.770 line:80%
I'm not misbehaving...

866
00:38:44.979 --> 00:38:47.229 line:80%
You set the condition, didn't you?

867
00:38:47.479 --> 00:38:48.854 line:80%
But his time's up.

868
00:38:48.937 --> 00:38:52.020 line:80%
- His time's up.
- Listen, just drop it and agree.

869
00:38:52.354 --> 00:38:53.979 line:80%
He got the job.

870
00:38:54.437 --> 00:38:55.604 line:80%
So my word doesn't matter?

871
00:38:55.687 --> 00:38:56.854 line:80%
And what about our dignity?

872
00:38:57.229 --> 00:38:59.562 line:80%
Dad...
Mom, I'm going to get ready.

873
00:38:59.645 --> 00:39:00.770 line:80%
Here, enjoy.

874
00:39:00.854 --> 00:39:02.354 line:80%
- Listen...
- Sister, let's go.

875
00:39:02.437 --> 00:39:03.187 line:80%
Titli!

876
00:39:03.354 --> 00:39:04.729 line:80%
- You'll regret this.
- Please, listen...

877
00:39:04.812 --> 00:39:06.520 line:80%
- Please hear me out.
- No. Come on, let's go.

878
00:39:07.020 --> 00:39:08.770 line:80%
What's going on? Go find out.

879
00:39:13.645 --> 00:39:14.854 line:80%
Get out of my way.

880
00:39:17.479 --> 00:39:19.604 line:80%
Sister-in-law, how are you?

881
00:39:19.687 --> 00:39:20.979 line:80%
- Congratulations,
- I'm fine.

882
00:39:21.062 --> 00:39:23.062 line:80%
- congratulations.
- You didn't have to bring all this.

883
00:39:23.145 --> 00:39:25.979 line:80%
- I really don't believe it...
- You go!

884
00:39:26.229 --> 00:39:27.979 line:80%
Our surprise is ruined.

885
00:39:28.062 --> 00:39:29.979 line:80%
- They already know!
- Here, take this.

886
00:39:30.479 --> 00:39:32.520 line:80%
Here, Brother, enjoy some sweets.

887
00:39:32.604 --> 00:39:33.854 line:80%
What's the occasion?

888
00:39:33.937 --> 00:39:35.104 line:80%
The wedding, of course.

889
00:39:35.520 --> 00:39:36.812 line:80%
It's not fixed yet.

890
00:39:36.895 --> 00:39:38.854 line:80%
It was fixed two months ago.

891
00:39:38.937 --> 00:39:40.312 line:80%
He just got the job.

892
00:39:40.854 --> 00:39:43.187 line:80%
Son, go seek her dad's blessings.

893
00:39:43.270 --> 00:39:44.645 line:80%
- Dad!
- No, no need.

894
00:39:44.729 --> 00:39:46.187 line:80%
He doesn't need to touch my feet.

895
00:39:46.270 --> 00:39:47.520 line:80%
Come here, son.
You can seek my blessings.

896
00:39:47.604 --> 00:39:48.604 line:80%
Mom...

897
00:39:48.687 --> 00:39:49.895 line:80%
This isn't right.

898
00:39:50.229 --> 00:39:50.979 line:80%
Let's go.

899
00:39:51.062 --> 00:39:53.562 line:80%
Just wait and see the electricity bill
you get this month.

900
00:39:53.645 --> 00:39:54.395 line:80%
Have it, have it.

901
00:39:54.479 --> 00:39:55.645 line:80%
- Chunne.
- Let's go.

902
00:39:55.979 --> 00:39:57.104 line:80%
Sir, I'll take my leave now.

903
00:39:57.187 --> 00:39:59.895 line:80%
Pundit-ji, which electricity bill
are you going to pay?

904
00:39:59.979 --> 00:40:00.979 line:80%
Please have a seat.

905
00:40:01.062 --> 00:40:03.270 line:80%
Shall we set the wedding date?

906
00:40:03.354 --> 00:40:05.562 line:80%
Yes, of course.
Yes, now you have to.

907
00:40:05.645 --> 00:40:07.104 line:80%
