it's already happened,

1131
00:50:40.895 --> 00:50:42.354 line:80%
but it hasn't. Got it?

1132
00:50:43.145 --> 00:50:44.020 line:80%
Really?

1133
00:50:45.062 --> 00:50:47.062 line:80%
So, what I saw was just
a super realistic dream?

1134
00:50:47.645 --> 00:50:49.312 line:80%
Yeah, looks like it.

1135
00:50:49.895 --> 00:50:50.729 line:80%
I see.

1136
00:50:50.812 --> 00:50:54.020 line:80%
So, you're saying today's the 29th,

1137
00:50:54.187 --> 00:50:55.895 line:80%
and tomorrow's the 30th, right?

1138
00:50:56.104 --> 00:50:57.312 line:80%
- Today's the 29th.
- Yeah.

1139
00:50:57.562 --> 00:50:59.062 line:80%
So, obviously, tomorrow's the 30th!

1140
00:50:59.645 --> 00:51:00.687 line:80%
Yep.

1141
00:51:00.979 --> 00:51:03.187 line:80%
Here, take Mom's petticoat
and get it dyed.

1142
00:51:03.270 --> 00:51:05.187 line:80%
- I don't run errands like that.
- Don't make a fuss, just go.

1143
00:51:05.270 --> 00:51:06.312 line:80%
Don't forget, okay?

1144
00:51:06.395 --> 00:51:07.479 line:80%
- Hey...
- Be careful with it. Bye!

1145
00:51:07.562 --> 00:51:08.729 line:80%
I've got a lot to do.

1146
00:51:10.729 --> 00:51:12.270 line:80%
Here's Mom's petticoat.

1147
00:51:12.354 --> 00:51:13.895 line:80%
- It needs to be dyed this color.
- Okay, Brother.

1148
00:51:15.395 --> 00:51:16.645 line:80%
Hey, what's the date today?

1149
00:51:16.812 --> 00:51:17.812 line:80%
29th, Brother.

1150
00:51:17.895 --> 00:51:18.895 line:80%
Why?

1151
00:51:19.187 --> 00:51:20.145 line:80%
Just checking.

1152
00:51:20.937 --> 00:51:21.895 line:80%
See you later.

1153
00:51:22.687 --> 00:51:23.854 line:80%
Mahadev!

1154
00:51:25.729 --> 00:51:27.020 line:80%
What's up, Brother?

1155
00:51:28.229 --> 00:51:29.895 line:80%
What's up, Mr. Groom?

1156
00:51:30.062 --> 00:51:31.437 line:80%
Where are you off to, huh?

1157
00:51:31.520 --> 00:51:33.020 line:80%
I just came to get Mom's petticoat dyed.

1158
00:51:33.062 --> 00:51:35.104 line:80%
- I know everything.
- Come on, man!

1159
00:51:35.187 --> 00:51:37.812 line:80%
Happy inside, acting shy outside, right?

1160
00:51:41.479 --> 00:51:42.645 line:80%
Damn it.

1161
00:51:47.229 --> 00:51:50.062 line:80%
It stinks like the cow
had radish parathas for dinner.

1162
00:51:50.395 --> 00:51:51.895 line:80%
Don't be so upset, Brother.

1163
00:51:52.229 --> 00:51:54.020 line:80%
This is the holy cow's blessings.

1164
00:51:54.062 --> 00:51:55.062 line:80%
- Really?
- Yeah.

1165
00:51:55.187 --> 00:51:56.020 line:80%
Her blessings, huh?

1166
00:51:56.187 --> 00:51:58.312 line:80%
- Well, here, you can have some too.
- Hey!

1167
00:51:59.187 --> 00:52:00.354 line:80%
Right.

1168
00:52:00.520 --> 00:52:02.270 line:80%
What's up, Mr. Groom?

1169
00:52:03.645 --> 00:52:08.020 line:80%
Hey, have they started using cow dung
instead of turmeric these days?

1170
00:52:08.104 --> 00:52:09.187 line:80%
Hey...

1171
00:52:09.270 --> 00:52:11.104 line:80%
Uncle, forget about that.

1172
00:52:11.229 --> 00:52:13.520 line:80%
Did you do what you went there to do?

1173
00:52:14.312 --> 00:52:16.062 line:80%
Everything's set, man.

1174
00:52:17.020 --> 00:52:18.520 line:80%
What's set? Tell me!

1175
00:52:18.854 --> 00:52:22.020 line:80%
Come on , Mr. Groom,
how can I tell you that

1176
00:52:22.104 --> 00:52:25.812 line:80%
we've arranged
a surprise bachelor's party for you.

1177
00:52:25.895 --> 00:52:27.229 line:80%
- A surprise party?
- Yeah.

1178
00:52:27.312 --> 00:52:28.187 line:80%
And I have no idea about it.

1179
00:52:28.270 --> 00:52:30.687 line:80%
Forget that and just get ready for it.

1180
00:52:30.770 --> 00:52:32.687 line:80%
- Har Har...
- Here.

1181
00:52:46.270 --> 00:52:49.729 line:80%
I enchant with my style,

1182
00:52:49.812 --> 00:52:53.229 line:80%
I remove every hesitation,

1183
00:52:53.312 --> 00:52:56.895 line:80%
Make me squirm

1184
00:52:57.020 --> 00:53:00.687 line:80%
with sweet pain, O heartless one.

1185
00:53:00.770 --> 00:53:02.395 line:80%
You seem dear to me,

1186
00:53:02.479 --> 00:53:04.187 line:80%
A sleeping intention is awakened,

1187
00:53:04.270 --> 00:53:06.062 line:80%
If you deny it, it's betrayal.

1188
00:53:07.770 --> 00:53:09.645 line:80%
Your eyes have misled me,

1189
00:53:09.729 --> 00:53:11.312 line:80%
This place seems desolate,

1190
00:53:11.395 --> 00:53:13.229 line:80%
My heart says...

1191
00:53:13.437 --> 00:53:16.812 line:80%
Beloved.

1192
00:53:16.895 --> 00:53:20.437 line:80%
Beloved.

1193
00:53:20.520 --> 00:53:23.770 line:80%
Beloved.

1194
00:53:24.687 --> 00:53:27.270 line:80%
Beloved.

1195
00:53:27.354 --> 00:53:30.645 line:80%
Enchant me with your charm,

1196
00:53:30.937 --> 00:53:34.104 line:80%
Make my forget the world, O fair one

1197
00:53:34.395 --> 00:53:38.020 line:80%
Your youth is like burning flames,

1198
00:53:38.062 --> 00:53:41.854 line:80%
In it, let me burn, O fair one

1199
00:53:42.479 --> 00:53:44.187 line:80%
I am fire, I am a flame,

1200
00:53:44.270 --> 00:53:46.020 line:80%
But I am also cool water.

1201
00:53:46.104 --> 00:53:47.854 line:80%
Today, I belong to you,

1202
00:53:47.937 --> 00:53:49.520 line:80%
But tomorrow, I will be a stranger.

1203
00:53:49.604 --> 00:53:51.312 line:80%
Lovers come to my doorstep,

1204
00:53:51.395 --> 00:53:53.062 line:80%
Thirsting for love...

1205
00:53:53.145 --> 00:53:54.937 line:80%
Spreading love, quench their thirst,

1206
00:53:54.979 --> 00:53:56.770 line:80%
That's what I do with my passion.

1207
00:53:56.854 --> 00:53:58.520 line:80%
That's what I do with my passion.

1208
00:53:58.604 --> 00:54:01.562 line:80%
Beloved.

1209
00:54:02.104 --> 00:54:04.854 line:80%
Beloved.

1210
00:54:05.020 --> 00:54:08.104 line:80%
Beloved.

1211
00:54:09.104 --> 00:54:11.979 line:80%
Beloved.

1212
00:54:44.437 --> 00:54:46.187 line:80%
Keep this box over there.

1213
00:54:46.312 --> 00:54:48.020 line:80%
Why are you carrying it over your head?

1214
00:54:48.104 --> 00:54:49.687 line:80%
Ma'am, where do you want me
to put this box of oil?

1215
00:54:49.770 --> 00:54:50.854 line:80%
Why don't you put it on my head?

1216
00:54:50.937 --> 00:54:52.312 line:80%
Obviously, you'll put it in the kitchen!

1217
00:54:52.395 --> 00:54:54.145 line:80%
I've been working non-stop...

1218
00:54:58.645 --> 00:55:03.229 line:80%
"In the turmeric, my dear,
in the turmeric..."

1219
00:55:03.312 --> 00:55:04.770 line:80%
It's this way. Come on now.

1220
00:55:04.854 --> 00:55:06.312 line:80%
You'll take two hours...

1221
00:55:32.729 --> 00:55:34.895 line:80%
What's wrong with my son?

1222
00:55:37.729 --> 00:55:39.437 line:80%
Move back, everyone,
let him get some fresh air.

1223
00:55:39.520 --> 00:55:40.895 line:80%
Move back, move back, everyone.

1224
00:55:41.062 --> 00:55:42.729 line:80%
- Yes, yes.
- He's starting to wake up.

1225
00:55:48.395 --> 00:55:49.104 line:80%
What's the date today?

1226
00:55:49.187 --> 00:55:50.104 line:80%
- Huh? Why?
- Why?

1227
00:55:50.187 --> 00:55:51.895 line:80%
What... what's the date today?!

1228
00:55:52.020 --> 00:55:52.854 line:80%
What happened?

1229
00:55:53.104 --> 00:55:55.020 line:80%
That's the problem,
Dad, it's not happening.

1230
00:55:55.104 --> 00:55:57.729 line:80%
I think he's constipated.
It's nothing new.

1231
00:55:57.812 --> 00:55:59.854 line:80%
Keri, my child, go get the laxatives.

1232
00:55:59.937 --> 00:56:01.312 line:80%
- Okay, Dad.
- Keri, Keri, Keri...

1233
00:56:01.645 --> 00:56:02.645 line:80%
What's today's date?

1234
00:56:02.729 --> 00:56:05.020 line:80%
- 29th... it's the 29th...
- 29th!

1235
00:56:05.270 --> 00:56:07.812 line:80%
Yesterday you said, "Today's the 29th,
and tomorrow's the 30th!"

1236
00:56:07.895 --> 00:56:08.604 line:80%
You said that yesterday, right?

1237
00:56:08.687 --> 00:56:10.062 line:80%
That's what I'm saying today.

1238
00:56:10.145 --> 00:56:11.437 line:80%
Today's the 29th, and tomorrow's the 30th.

1239
00:56:11.520 --> 00:56:12.812 line:80%
No, you said that yesterday.

1240
00:56:12.895 --> 00:56:14.687 line:80%
Yesterday was the 29th,
so today would be the 30th, right?

1241
00:56:14.770 --> 00:56:15.812 line:80%
- What are you saying?
- I told you...

1242
00:56:15.895 --> 00:56:16.937 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

1243
00:56:17.020 --> 00:56:20.562 line:80%
I told you not to let him out
of the house until the wedding.

1244
00:56:20.645 --> 00:56:24.229 line:80%
- He's been possessed.
- I'm not possessed, Mom!

1245
00:56:24.312 --> 00:56:25.562 line:80%
How do I...

1246
00:56:27.270 --> 00:56:28.395 line:80%
Huh?

1247
00:56:28.895 --> 00:56:30.812 line:80%
- Turmeric!
- He's lost it.

1248
00:56:30.895 --> 00:56:33.229 line:80%
We're back to the turmeric
ceremony again, seriously?!

1249
00:56:34.062 --> 00:56:35.520 line:80%
How do I explain this to you?

1250
00:56:36.562 --> 00:56:37.229 line:80%
This...

1251
00:56:37.312 --> 00:56:38.437 line:80%
What?

1252
00:56:39.687 --> 00:56:41.062 line:80%
Mom, come with me.

1253
00:56:41.145 --> 00:56:41.729 line:80%
What happened?

1254
00:56:41.812 --> 00:56:42.645 line:80%
- Dad?
- Yeah?

1255
00:56:42.729 --> 00:56:43.437 line:80%
Come with me.

1256
00:56:43.604 --> 00:56:44.437 line:80%
What is it?
Move aside.

1257
00:56:44.604 --> 00:56:45.979 line:80%
- What is it?
- This flower pot?

1258
00:56:46.020 --> 00:56:46.770 line:80%
Yeah?

1259
00:56:46.854 --> 00:56:47.604 line:80%
Look at it.

1260
00:56:47.687 --> 00:56:48.812 line:80%
We're looking at it.

1261
00:56:49.354 --> 00:56:50.312 line:80%
Keep looking at it.

1262
00:56:51.229 --> 00:56:52.187 line:80%
Hey...

1263
00:56:53.937 --> 00:56:54.729 line:80%
This flower pot...

1264
00:56:54.812 --> 00:56:55.812 line:80%
- Yeah?
- Yeah?

1265
00:56:56.187 --> 00:56:57.145 line:80%
It's going to fall.

1266
00:56:57.604 --> 00:56:58.687 line:80%
It will fall on its own?

1267
00:56:58.770 --> 00:56:59.895 line:80%
It'll fall now. Just wait and watch.

1268
00:57:00.020 --> 00:57:00.895 line:80%
Hey...

1269
00:57:00.979 --> 00:57:01.770 line:80%
When is it going to fall, son?

1270
00:57:01.854 --> 00:57:02.812 line:80%
We're getting late
for the turmeric ceremony.

1271
00:57:02.895 --> 00:57:03.979 line:80%
Not the turmeric ceremony again!

1272
00:57:04.020 --> 00:57:05.187 line:80%
Don't ever mention it again!

1273
00:57:05.270 --> 00:57:06.562 line:80%
I don't want any turmeric paste on me!

1274
00:57:06.645 --> 00:57:07.604 line:80%
Huh?

1275
00:57:08.020 --> 00:57:09.062 line:80%
Fall...

1276
00:57:10.937 --> 00:57:12.770 line:80%
- Fall...
- How can it fall on its own?

1277
00:57:12.979 --> 00:57:13.979 line:80%
Fall...

1278
00:57:14.604 --> 00:57:16.104 line:80%
It falls!

1279
00:57:16.520 --> 00:57:19.062 line:80%
- When will it fall? My neck's hurting.
- It'll fall soon!

1280
00:57:19.937 --> 00:57:21.395 line:80%
Where's the decorator?

1281
00:57:21.854 --> 00:57:22.479 line:80%
There he is.

1282
00:57:22.562 --> 00:57:25.312 line:80%
Hey, what are you doing here?
Go do your job. Go, go, go.

1283
00:57:25.687 --> 00:57:26.895 line:80%
- Yeah.
- You put up flowers every day, don't you?

1284
00:57:26.979 --> 00:57:28.062 line:80%
- Yeah.
- Go, put the flowers up.

1285
00:57:28.312 --> 00:57:30.229 line:80%
- Now you watch, it'll fall.
- Okay, okay.

1286
00:57:30.520 --> 00:57:32.479 line:80%
When's it going to fall, Your Highness?

1287
00:57:32.562 --> 00:57:33.437 line:80%
It'll fall, Dad.

1288
00:57:39.520 --> 00:57:40.687 line:80%
Start working already!

1289
00:57:41.187 --> 00:57:43.020 line:80%
Brother, if everyone's going
to stare at me,

1290
00:57:43.104 --> 00:57:44.145 line:80%
I'm going to get nervous.

1291
00:57:44.229 --> 00:57:46.020 line:80%
It's not like I'm asking you
to sing a song,

1292
00:57:46.437 --> 00:57:47.979 line:80%
so why would you get nervous?
Just do your job.

1293
00:57:48.062 --> 00:57:48.979 line:80%
Okay, I'm doing it.

1294
00:57:49.479 --> 00:57:51.312 line:80%
Not the ones in the back,
the flowers in the front.

1295
00:57:51.395 --> 00:57:53.562 line:80%
- Yes, yes.
- Fine, I'm doing it, I'm doing it.

1296
00:57:54.312 --> 00:57:57.437 line:80%
Reduce the gap!
Or I'll use my sandals on you!

1297
00:57:59.312 --> 00:58:00.395 line:80%
It fell!

1298
00:58:00.729 --> 00:58:02.145 line:80%
It fell! It fell!

1299
00:58:02.312 --> 00:58:03.854 line:80%
This is the one! I told you!

1300
00:58:03.979 --> 00:58:05.729 line:80%
I told you it would fall, and it fell!

1301
00:58:05.812 --> 00:58:09.312 line:80%
Great magic trick, son.

1302
00:58:10.895 --> 00:58:12.645 line:80%
Now you want me to show you
a magic trick of my own?

1303
00:58:12.729 --> 00:58:13.187 line:80%
Magic?

1304
00:58:13.270 --> 00:58:15.395 line:80%
Yeah, you said the flower pot would...

1305
00:58:15.895 --> 00:58:17.354 line:80%
- Fall?
- It would fall.

1306
00:58:17.437 --> 00:58:18.604 line:80%
And what's this?

1307
00:58:18.770 --> 00:58:20.812 line:80%
- Your hand.
- Now you...

1308
00:58:23.770 --> 00:58:25.312 line:80%
Move your head forward.

1309
00:58:26.520 --> 00:58:27.729 line:80%
I'll go blind.

1310
00:58:28.270 --> 00:58:29.812 line:80%
How else is he supposed to check?

1311
00:58:30.520 --> 00:58:32.020 line:80%
Unnecessary drama.

1312
00:58:33.687 --> 00:58:35.812 line:80%
So, you think yesterday was the 29th too?

1313
00:58:35.895 --> 00:58:36.645 line:80%
Yeah.

1314
00:58:36.729 --> 00:58:38.270 line:80%
And what was the date the day
before yesterday?

1315
00:58:38.937 --> 00:58:40.812 line:80%
The day before yesterday
was also the 29th.

1316
00:58:41.604 --> 00:58:43.020 line:80%
If yesterday was the 29th,

1317
00:58:43.104 --> 00:58:45.270 line:80%
then the day before yesterday
should've been the 28th, right?

1318
00:58:46.187 --> 00:58:48.312 line:80%
He's terrible at math, really bad.

1319
00:58:48.562 --> 00:58:50.729 line:80%
He's always been bad at math.

1320
00:58:50.812 --> 00:58:52.979 line:80%
You've always had a problem with my math.

1321
00:58:53.062 --> 00:58:54.270 line:80%
Why didn't you send me
for extra coaching then?

1322
00:58:54.354 --> 00:58:56.104 line:80%
I was going to, but...

1323
00:58:56.270 --> 00:58:58.187 line:80%
I've been living the 29th
for two days now,

1324
00:58:58.270 --> 00:58:59.270 line:80%
and the day just won't change to the 30th.

1325
00:58:59.354 --> 00:59:00.604 line:80%
Why doesn't anyone get it?

1326
00:59:00.854 --> 00:59:02.270 line:80%
Why are you crying?

1327
00:59:02.437 --> 00:59:04.312 line:80%
The doctor says
everything's going to be fine.

1328
00:59:04.395 --> 00:59:05.729 line:80%
How is everything going to be fine?

1329
00:59:05.812 --> 00:59:07.354 line:80%
He's lost his mind,
and tomorrow's his wedding.

1330
00:59:08.104 --> 00:59:09.187 line:80%
I've lost my mind?

1331
00:59:11.104 --> 00:59:13.104 line:80%
- Put it on speaker.
- Okay.

1332
00:59:13.312 --> 00:59:14.229 line:80%
Hello?

1333
00:59:14.520 --> 00:59:15.479 line:80%
Hello, Sister-in-law.
I seek your blessings.

1334
00:59:15.562 --> 00:59:16.229 line:80%
What happened?

1335
00:59:16.312 --> 00:59:18.104 line:80%
Keri said you guys went to the doctor?

1336
00:59:18.187 --> 00:59:20.770 line:80%
Nothing happened, Ranjan's just...

1337
00:59:21.020 --> 00:59:22.812 line:80%
What? I'm coming there.

1338
00:59:22.895 --> 00:59:24.354 line:80%
No, Sister-in-law.
You don't need to come here.

1339
00:59:24.437 --> 00:59:25.562 line:80%
Don't worry about it.

1340
00:59:25.979 --> 00:59:26.979 line:80%
Hello?

1341
00:59:27.895 --> 00:59:29.354 line:80%
You're impossible.

1342
00:59:29.812 --> 00:59:31.812 line:80%
What, Uncle, I didn't tell her anything.

1343
00:59:32.020 --> 00:59:34.187 line:80%
Hey, hey, hey,
where do you think you're going?

1344
00:59:34.270 --> 00:59:36.145 line:80%
Hey, what's got him worked up now?

1345
00:59:36.229 --> 00:59:37.270 line:80%
Nephew!

1346
00:59:37.354 --> 00:59:39.395 line:80%
Listen, nephew! Just hear me out!

1347
00:59:39.520 --> 00:59:40.562 line:80%
Brother!

1348
00:59:41.312 --> 00:59:43.604 line:80%
Brother!
Getting angry isn't going to help!

1349
00:59:43.687 --> 00:59:45.187 line:80%
Just listen to me, Nephew.

1350
00:59:45.479 --> 00:59:47.312 line:80%
I don't want to be checked by that quack.

1351
00:59:48.020 --> 00:59:50.854 line:80%
Everyone in Banaras knows he's just
a compounder pretending to be a doctor,

1352
00:59:50.937 --> 00:59:52.062 line:80%
and you took me to him?

1353
00:59:52.145 --> 00:59:54.187 line:80%
Then let's go to BHU, Brother.

1354
00:59:54.479 --> 00:59:56.729 line:80%
I'll slap you so hard you'll have
a tattoo on your face.

1355
00:59:57.562 --> 00:59:59.229 line:80%
Do I look sick to you?

1356
00:59:59.312 --> 01:00:00.312 line:80%
Do I?

1357
01:00:00.687 --> 01:00:03.895 line:80%
